  "texts": [
    "The experiment is structured in two parts: dataset creation and API classification evaluation.",
    "A. Dataset GenerationWe generate datasets for six API modules commonly found in modern web and mobile applications: Calculator, Notes, Weather, Email, Notification, and Calendar.",
    "These modules are selected for their widespread applicability across various software systems, representing a diverse range of API functionalities.",
    "They span from basic arithmetic operations to more complex language-based tasks, ensuring comprehensive coverage of typical API interactions.",
    "For each of these modules, we simulate several commonly used functions, each corresponding to distinct operations or actions."
  ],
